data.description: Updated and remodeled home  CHARMING , COZY AND GORGEOUS TOWNHOME with 3 Bedrooms & 3.5 Full Baths, WONT LAST!!!! Monthly HOA Fee is $150.00 and includes sewer, trash, water, exterior and interior  landscaping. This house is also equipped with a water purification system.
